# Medical Test Records Management System Requirements

## FRONTEND (React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS)
Directory: /frontend

### Core Features:
1. Landing Page
   - Implement smooth scroll animations using Framer Motion
   - Hero section with medical-themed video background from Pexels
   - Features section with fade-in animations
   - Authentication components (Sign in/Sign up/Password reset)
   - ARIA-compliant accessible components
   - Responsive navigation with mobile menu

2. Patient Dashboard
   - Protected routes with role-based authentication
   - Summary cards with gradient overlays showing key metrics
   - Interactive data visualization using Recharts/Chart.js
   - Test record management interface with:
     * Filterable data tables
     * Time-series graphs
     * Trend analysis charts
     * CSV export functionality
   - Add/Edit test records with categorized input forms
   - Responsive grid layouts for all screen sizes

3. Future Extensions
   - Doctor portal (placeholder routes)
   - Admin dashboard (placeholder routes)
   - User management interface

## BACKEND (FastAPI + PostgreSQL)
Directory: /backend

### API Features:
1. Authentication
   - JWT-based auth system
   - Password hashing with bcrypt
   - Refresh token rotation
   - Password reset flow

2. Core Endpoints
   - CRUD operations for test records
   - Data aggregation for visualizations
   - User management
   - Role-based access control

3. Database
   - Async PostgreSQL with SQLAlchemy
   - Data validation with Pydantic
   - Migration system with Alembic

## DOCKER
Root directory: docker-compose.yml
- Frontend container (Node.js)
- Backend container (Python)
- PostgreSQL container
- Nginx reverse proxy
- Development and production configurations

## Technical Requirements:
- TypeScript strict mode
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
- Comprehensive test coverage
- API documentation with Swagger
- Error handling and logging
- Security best practices
- Performance optimization

## Test Panels Supported:
A. Complete Blood Count (CBC): RBC, HB, PLATELETS, WBC
B. Kidney Function Test (KFT): POTASSIUM, UREA, CREATININE, eGFR
C. Liver Function Test (LFT): ALT, AST, ALP, GGT, T-BIL, D-BIL, TOTAL PROTEIN, ALBUMIN
D. Lipid Profile: T. CHOL, HDL, LDL, TRIG, NON-HDL CHOL
E. Glucose Panel: GLUCOSE, HBA1C, INSULIN, LACTATE
F. Iron Panel: IRON, TRANSFERRI, FERRITIN, IRON SATURATION
G. Fluid: PROTEIN, GLUCOSE, LDH
H. Cardiac Enzymes: CPK, AST, LDH, CKMB
I. Tropinins: T. I, T. T
J. Thyroid Function Test: TSH, T3, T4
K. Urine Routine Examination: PROTEIN, BLOOD, BACTERIA, SG, GLUCOSE
L. Basic Fertilities: FSH, LH, PROLACTIN, ESTROGEN, PROGESTERONE, AMH, TESTOSTERONE
M. Electrolytes: SODIUM, POTASSIUM, CHLORIDE
N. Semen Analysis: Sperm concentration, Motility, Sperm count, Viability
O. ACR: Albumin, Creatinine, Ratio
P. Urine Protein Creatinine Ratio: URINE CREATININE, URINE PROTEIN, RATIO